entries.title: Exclusive: Surveillance Footage of Tesla Crash on SF’s Bay Bridge Hours After Elon Musk Announces "Self-Driving" Feature
entries.description:
Musk has said Tesla’s problematic autopilot features are “really the difference between Tesla being worth a lot of money or worth basically zero.”

The post Exclusive: Surveillance Footage of Tesla Crash on SF’s Bay Bridge Hours After Elon Musk Announces “Self-Driving” Feature appeared first on The Intercept.

entries.title: Those Russian Twitter Bots Didn't Do $#!% in 2016, Says New Study
entries.description:
There is "no evidence" Russian Twitter bots had any meaningful effect pushing voters to Donald Trump in the 2016 presidential election.

The post Those Russian Twitter Bots Didn’t Do $#!% in 2016, Says New Study appeared first on The Intercept.

entries.title: House Rules Package Gives Democrats a Path to Averting a Debt Ceiling Crisis
entries.description:
Republicans preserved the discharge petition in the new rules package, allowing any bill with 218 votes to come to the floor — even one codifying Roe v. Wade.

The post House Rules Package Gives Democrats a Path to Averting a Debt Ceiling Crisis appeared first on The Intercept.
